Ronaldo wey be 55 years, dem dey call am di senior managing director for Gruntal & Co.Broders subsidiary of dis insurance, and financial service firm.

Mr. Koenig go build corporate bank, wey be sey na ekrone and investment bank wey be sey na ekrone.

Na im be di chairman and co-chief executive for Ladenburg, Thalmann & Co until July wey dem dey call am cochairman of investment bank, along with Howard L. Blum Jr na im come be di only oga for di bank.

Oga, yesterday, Mr. Blum, 41 e no know sey plan dey for Ladenburg to name co-chairman to succeed Oga, Koenig, and sey di board go need to approve any appointment, and title change.

Oga Blum add sey e no surprise Oga, Koenig resign o, but im departure na nothing wey we want, or work for. Oga, Koenig talk sey I just receive one kind big, big contribution from Gruntal.

